---
title: Dukkah Chicken and Orange Salad with Crispy Chickpeas
description: Roasted herbaceous chicken breasts are draped over spinach, arugula and orange slices then treated with a drizzle of zesty shallot vinaigrette. To top it all off, you get a healthy dose of crispy baked chickpeas!

